@achowdhery Thank you for your concern. I am unable to upload here all files due to limited upload permission. Sorry for the inconvenience, I am attaching here 2 different folders. Each following folder contains below files.

  1. Source_file1: detect.tflite, label_map.txt and pipeline.config
  2. Source_file2: tflite_graph.pb

Checkpoint file for 10000 training steps is of file size 44.7 Mb, which I am unable to upload due to limited upload permissions from GitHub.

The model is quantized version and I have downloaded it from tensorflow zoo directory. The folder name is "ssd_mobilenet_v1_quantized_coco".

I had also tried with ssd_mobilenet_0.75_quantized_coco, but after training no detection on the detect app. However, when I am checking the trained model using webcam it is working fine for both the models.

Thank you for your time.

source_files1.tar.gz
source_file2.tar.gz

body:
@achowdhery Thank you for your concern. I am unable to upload here all files due to limited upload permission. Sorry for the inconvenience, I am attaching here 2 different folders. Each following folder contains below files.
1. Source_file1: detect.tflite, label_map.txt and pipeline.config
2. Source_file2: tflite_graph.pb

Checkpoint file for 10000 training steps is of file size 44.7 Mb, which I am unable to upload due to limited upload permissions from GitHub.

The model is quantized version and I have downloaded it from tensorflow zoo directory. The folder name is "ssd_mobilenet_v1_quantized_coco".


I had also tried with ssd_mobilenet_0.75_quantized_coco, but after training no detection on the detect app. However, when I am checking the trained model using webcam it is working fine for both the models.

Thank you for your time.

[source_file2.tar.gz](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/files/2326695/source_file2.tar.gz)
